                                                                <p class="mb-1"><span class="fw-semibold me-2">Address:</span> 3559 Roosevelt Wilson Lane San Bernardino, CA 92405</p>
                                                                <p class="mb-1"><span class="fw-semibold me-2">Phone:</span> (123) 456-7890</p>
